{"tid":629781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【網民hot talk】強國教友烏溪沙滅絕式掘蜆 居民趕到制止","createTime":"2018-04-15T04:02:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-16T09:22:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b360050b1cccca3251e03ba4915528128b9e3ac9","tid":629781,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/120125_2fc9e18567415cf54c593a793e3fb440.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F120125_2fc9e18567415cf54c593a793e3fb440.png&h=cd9e7cac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/120143_52200cc4ac0d7c935615bed814ef61ad.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F120143_52200cc4ac0d7c935615bed814ef61ad.png&h=6a566dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/15/120151_6342a04c7bcbe5228605e03fd39b41ee.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F15%2F120151_6342a04c7bcbe5228605e03fd39b41ee.png&h=47e33931&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n馬鞍山烏溪沙石灘除「心型石」引起不少爭議外，近日疑有內地教友在該處大肆掘蜆，被批評破壞生態環境，有關注組織成員趕至現場，成功阻止對方帶走裝滿整個膠箱的蜆。<br />\n<br />\n由馬鞍山居民自發組成的團體「烏溪沙石灘海岸關注組」facebook群組，昨午上載數張照片，顯示有一群穿着「Lamb of God」字樣上衣的人在烏溪沙石灘掘蜆，其中一張照片更見到掘出的蜆放滿一大個膠箱。帖文指，關注組成員趕至現場了解，得知掘蜆者是內地團體「聖血愛浸禮教會」的成員，他們此行是參與烏溪沙青年營活動。經關注組成員講解後，他們願意將蜆及數條罕見的大海蔘放回石灘。<br />\n<br />\n該關注組其中一名管理員留言表示，當時曾問該批內地人為何要掘蜆，對方回覆為了「玩樂」。關注組強調，對損害生命及大自然來玩樂的行為「絕對是零容忍」。<br />\n<br />\n關注組向《蘋果》透露，昨午約3時許見到約40人在烏溪沙掘蜆，除了裝滿大膠箱，另有部分人手持細盤，同樣裝滿蜆，「有大（蜆）有細（蜆）」。雖然平日也有人會到石灘，例如家長帶子女認識大自然，但鮮有這麼誇張地掘蜆。<br />\n<br />\n每年4月至10月是摸蜆的旺季，逢周末假日都有人到烏溪沙一帶的石灘掘蜆，不少家長帶備掘沙工具，帶同子女到場，玩足一個下午，但少見掘出如此大數量的蜆，亦較少人會取走食用。<br />\n<br />\n網民留言：<br />\nEric Yuen：什麼教？ 會不尊重其他生命？<br />\nChan Yuk Ying：所以大家會睇到一些內地人去參觀花或果園，見到旁邊的植物便大刺刺的摘取，而這些植物是農夫辛勞栽種的成果。總之見到任何物資，在內地人眼中都是可以拿取的！他們眼中只有自己，完無不知道地球上有其他人類，有生物，而生物都是天跌下來給他們拿回家或吃落肚的<br />\nHoma Ho：掘到食完先係問題，同用屎坑水煮飯一樣。冇腦<br />\nWilliam Wong：感謝主。香港可以任意破壞<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》沙士15周年系列網站，正式登場：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=db0db309\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fsars15&h=b0bfb531\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/sars15</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180415/58073891\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F58073891&d=e2PC5uQKZy0AmFTAHjyWpv1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=c9e6dac5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180415%2F58073891&h=bba8a980\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180415/58073891</a>"},{"pid":"118ed8758a37a21baa3df75bcc62da8409b57d10","tid":629781,"uid":135767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:05:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3cd62393bb9f8c65887702e9a8363d77154ffd49","tid":629781,"uid":57513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:08:40.000Z","msg":"成箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n掘兩三隻就話jer,<br />\n蝗蟲真係蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fb934d879fe115597197206d49bb23b1f6c3964","tid":629781,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cd62393bb9f8c65887702e9a8363d77154ffd49","tid":629781,"uid":57513,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-15T04:08:40.000Z","msg":"成箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n掘兩三隻就話jer,<br />\n蝗蟲真係蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad